At eto naisip ko...

124
00:10:21,412 --> 00:10:23,831
Sinasabi lang,
pero wag kang tumingin sa iba.

125
00:10:23,914 --> 00:10:24,915
Sige.

126
00:10:51,442 --> 00:10:52,610
Se-ah.

127
